   Monthly Tourism Statistics

   This section of the web site provides the most up-to-date monthly
   figures available on arrival and departure information to and from the
   U.S. Each month TI up dates this section of the web site - so "bookmark
   this page and come back for monthly updates."

   Please select from one of the following sections:

   Arrivals to the U.S.

   U.S. Outbound Travel by World Regions

   Quarterly U.S. International Travel Receipts and Payments
